examples.en: They have a house of their own.
examples.ru: У них есть свой собственный дом.

examples.en: The birds have left their nest.
Every one in the house were in their beds.

examples.en: He was angry because of their arriving late.
examples.ru: Он был зол, потому что их прибытие задерживалось.

examples.en: All the furniture in their house is brand-new.

examples.en: John and Mary have announced their engagement.

examples.en: The trees have all shed their leaves.
These boys know their Greek syntax.

examples.en: They are on friendly terms with their neighbors.
examples.ru: Они находятся в дружеских отношениях со своими соседями.

examples.en: The students are seeking to exercise their rights.
